<h4 class = "page-header">Create Development Directory</h4>
<p>
  Lets make a directory on our desktop and call it "development". Be sure to change directories into Desktop before making the directory.
  <pre>mkdir development</pre>
</p>
<p>
  Within the development directory lets create a new file
  <pre>touch intro.rb</pre>
</p>
<p>Moving forward always create your files and directories via the terminal.</p>
